  "bio_raw": "Ms. Liliping worked in Corporate division and Credit Administration department of IDLC finance Limited for five years. She looked after financing extended to corporate and SME clients in various sectors.\nBesides her regular job responsibilities she was a core team member of banking software migration project undertaken by IDLC finance limited. She led the Credit Administration department during the software implementation project.\nIn 2013, she got an opportunity to pursue Masters in Australia. It was awarded by the Australian Government under Australia Awards scholarship program.\nAt present, she is teaching finance and accounting courses in the school of business of ULAB.",
  "stated_interests": [
    "Economy, Development, Corporate Financing, SME Financing, Financial Inclusion"
  ],
